                    <h1 class="media-heading" style="font-family: Gabriola; color: #34a58e; "><b>Allergist</b></h1>
                    <p style="color: black; font-size: 15px; font-family: 'Adobe Kaiti Std'; color: #333; ">Allergists work with a wide variety of patients who suffer from issues related to allergies, such as hay, fever, or asthma. They are specially trained to treat these issues and assist patients in dealing with them and what to do when they are encountered.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="media">
                <div class="media-body">
                    <h1 class="media-heading" style="font-family: Gabriola; color: #34a58e; "><b> Dentist</b></h1>
                    <p style="color: black; font-size: 15px; font-family: 'Adobe Kaiti Std';color: #333">Dentists work with the human mouth, examining teeth and gum health and preventing and detecting various different issues, such as cavities and bleeding gums. Typically, patients are advised to go to the dentist twice a year in order to maintain tooth health.</pstyle>
                </div>
                <div class="media-right">
                    <img src="/images/tooth.jpg" class="pic">
                    <img src="/images/tooth.jpg" class="picbig">
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="media">
                <div class="media-left">
                    <img src="/images/ear.jpg" class="pic">
