                </div>
                <div class="media-body">
                    <h1 class="media-heading" style="font-family: Gabriola; color: #34a58e; "><b> Audiologist</b></h1>
                    <p style="color: black; font-size: 15px; font-family: 'Adobe Kaiti Std';color: #333">Audiologists specialize in ear related issues, particularly with regard to hearing loss in children. These doctors work with deaf and mute children to assist in their learning to communicate. They typically work in hospitals, physicians’ offices, audiology clinics, and occasionally in schools.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <div class="media">
                <div class="media-body">
                    <h1 class="media-heading" style="font-family: Gabriola; color: #34a58e; "><b> Cardiologist</b></h1>
                    <p style="color: black; font-size: 15px; font-family: 'Adobe Kaiti Std';color: #333">Cardiologists specify in the study and treatment of the heart and the many diseases and issues related to it. They assess the medical and family history of patients to determine potential risk for certain cardiovascular diseases and take action to prevent them.</p>
                </div>
